precis:
HUMAN PATHOGENS IMPORTATION REGULATIONS requiring that a person importing
a human pathogen (an infectious substance or the toxin of an infectious
substance) into Canada comply with safety standards with respect to
laboratory facilities for the handling, containment and disposal of the
organism.
